list.name: Shrimply Pibbles
list.about: Shrimply Pibbles is a highly respected and influential figure in the galaxy. Despite being a small crustacean-like creature, Shrimply Pibbles possesses a vast intellect and has dedicated his life to promoting peace and understanding among different species. He has mediated in countless interstellar conflicts and has successfully brokered peace treaties that have saved millions of lives. Shrimply Pibbles' wise and compassionate nature has earned him the title of 'The Diplomat of the Cosmos.'

list.name: Simple Rick
list.about: Simple Rick, the humble and content version of Rick Sanchez, lives a simple life outside the complexities of the multiverse. He spends his days creating delicious homemade cookies and singing cheerful songs. Simple Rick's unique brainwave pattern is used to make a special blend of joy known as 'Simple Rick's Simple Wafers.' Consuming these wafers allows individuals to experience the pure happiness and satisfaction of Simple Rick's uncomplicated existence.

list.name: Slaveowner
list.about: The character known as Slaveowner is a fictional persona within the context of the 'Gazorpazorpfield' TV show in the Rick and Morty universe. Slaveowner represents a satirical commentary on problematic and outdated cultural representations. The character's exaggerated portrayal is intended to provoke critical reflection on the harmful stereotypes perpetuated by certain forms of media. The inclusion of Slaveowner serves as a reminder of the importance of conscious storytelling and challenging harmful narratives.

list.name: Sleepy Gary
list.about: Sleepy Gary is an undercover agent from the Galactic Federation who infiltrated the Smith family's lives to gather intelligence. Despite his deceptive appearance as an ordinary, sleepy husband, Sleepy Gary possesses remarkable espionage skills. He can seamlessly blend into any environment and extract information without raising suspicion. Sleepy Gary's ability to maintain his cover for an extended period without detection has made him a legendary figure within the Galactic Federation's intelligence community.

list.name: Slick Morty
list.about: Slick Morty is a Morty from an alternate dimension where everyone has an incredibly smooth and slicked-back hairstyle. The unique hair genetics of Slick Morty's dimension have given him the ability to secrete a specialized hair gel that grants him enhanced agility and slipperiness. This allows him to evade capture and escape from even the most dire situations. Slick Morty's distinctive appearance and elusive nature have made him a sought-after companion for adventures in the multiverse.

list.name: Slippery Stair
list.about: Slippery Stair is a mysterious character who exists solely as a physical embodiment of chaos and unpredictability. Wherever Slippery Stair goes, reality becomes unstable, and the laws of physics become unpredictable. Gravity can fluctuate, objects can change shape, and cause-and-effect relationships can be inverted. Interacting with Slippery Stair is a constant exercise in adapting to an ever-shifting environment. Their presence challenges the very foundations of order and stability in the multiverse.

list.name: Slow Mobius
list.about: Slow Mobius is a member of the Time Variance Authority (TVA) and is responsible for managing and maintaining the proper flow of time in various dimensions. As his name suggests, Slow Mobius has the ability to control the speed of time within his immediate vicinity. This power allows him to investigate temporal anomalies and ensure that the timeline remains intact. Slow Mobius' calm and methodical nature makes him an invaluable asset in preserving the stability of the multiverse.

list.name: Slow Rick
list.about: Slow Rick is a version of Rick Sanchez from an alternate dimension where time moves at an incredibly slow pace. Due to the sluggish flow of time, Slow Rick has had ample opportunities to study and master complex scientific concepts. His slow and deliberate approach to problem-solving has allowed him to make groundbreaking discoveries that would take other Ricks years or even centuries to achieve. Slow Rick's patience and meticulousness have earned him a reputation as one of the most brilliant minds in the multiverse.

list.name: Snuffles (Snowball)
list.about: Snuffles, also known as Snowball, is Morty's pet dog who gains enhanced intelligence after using a device created by Rick. With his newfound intelligence, Snuffles leads a revolution of sentient dogs, demanding equal rights and freedom from human oppression. Snuffles' plight highlights themes of societal power dynamics and the consequences of underestimating other species' capabilities. His story serves as a cautionary tale about the potential consequences of exploiting or mistreating animals.

list.name: Solicitor Rick
list.about: Solicitor Rick is a version of Rick Sanchez who specializes in legal matters and serves as a solicitor for various interdimensional clients. His expertise in navigating the intricacies of interdimensional law and loopholes allows him to assist clients in resolving complex legal disputes. Solicitor Rick's sharp intellect and persuasive arguments have made him a formidable force in the courtroom. Despite his focus on legal matters, he still retains his characteristic cynicism and irreverence.

list.name: Squanchy
list.about: Squanchy is a cat-like creature from the planet Squanch and is known for his eccentric behavior and unique vocabulary. Squanchy's language, known as 'Squanch,' consists mostly of variations of the word 'squanch,' which can convey a wide range of emotions and intentions depending on the context. His peculiar manner of speaking has gained popularity among fans of the show, with 'squanch' becoming a catchphrase synonymous with Squanchy's quirky personality.

list.name: Stacy
list.about: Stacy is a minor character in the Rick and Morty universe, known for her impeccable fashion sense and style. Despite her limited screen time, Stacy has become an icon of fashion inspiration for many viewers. Fans of the show often discuss and recreate Stacy's outfits, showcasing their creativity and passion for fashion. Stacy's influence extends beyond the show, with her fashion choices inspiring real-world trends and becoming a symbol of self-expression and individuality.

list.name: Stair Goblin
list.about: Stair Goblin is a mischievous creature that dwells within the interdimensional portals hidden in staircases. They possess the ability to manipulate gravity and create disorienting staircases that seemingly defy the laws of physics. Stair Goblin's pranks have caused countless individuals to stumble, trip, and question their sanity. Legend has it that offering Stair Goblin a small trinket or token of appreciation can appease them, ensuring a smooth and hazard-free journey up or down the stairs.

list.name: Stealy
list.about: Stealy is a kleptomaniac alien who has a peculiar obsession with stealing valuable objects. He possesses an uncanny knack for pilfering rare and valuable artifacts from across the multiverse. Stealy's collection includes items of immense historical and cultural significance, making him a notorious figure in the criminal underworld. Despite his criminal tendencies, Stealy's exploits have inadvertently led to the recovery and preservation of lost treasures, making him a complex and morally ambiguous character.

list.name: Steve
list.about: Steve is an ordinary guy who happened to cross paths with Rick and Morty during their interdimensional adventures. Despite his lack of exceptional abilities or unique traits, Steve's presence in the show serves as a reminder of the vastness and unpredictability of the multiverse. His ordinary life contrasts with the extraordinary events unfolding around him, highlighting the juxtaposition between the mundane and the extraordinary in the Rick and Morty universe.

list.name: Steven Phillips
list.about: Steven Phillips is an interdimensional explorer who has ventured to the farthest reaches of the multiverse. Equipped with advanced technology and an insatiable curiosity, Steven has documented countless unique worlds and encountered extraordinary beings. His discoveries have expanded the knowledge of the multiverse and pushed the boundaries of scientific understanding. Steven's explorations have become a source of inspiration for aspiring interdimensional travelers and have sparked new avenues of research in the field of multiverse studies.

list.name: Stu
list.about: Stu is a background character in the Rick and Morty universe who has gained a cult following among fans of the show. Despite having no significant role or dialogue, Stu's presence in various episodes has sparked countless fan theories and speculations. Fans have created intricate backstories and interpretations for Stu, turning him into a beloved enigma within the fandom. Stu's mysterious nature has become a symbol of the show's intricate and multilayered storytelling.

list.name: Summer Smith
list.about: Summer Smith is one of the main characters in Rick and Morty, known for her growth and development throughout the series. Initially portrayed as a typical teenager, Summer evolves into a multifaceted character, displaying intelligence, bravery, and resilience. Her journey highlights the complexities of adolescence and the challenges of finding one's identity in a chaotic multiverse. Summer's character arc has resonated with viewers, inspiring discussions about personal growth and empowerment.

list.name: Summer Smith
list.about: Summer Smith, Morty's older sister, is a character who undergoes significant growth and transformation over the course of the series. Initially depicted as a stereotypical teenage girl, Summer evolves into a strong, independent individual who embraces her own agency and makes her mark on the multiverse. Summer's character development explores themes of self-discovery, identity, and the importance of forging one's path in a world full of possibilities.

list.name: Supernova
list.about: Supernova is a powerful superheroine who possesses the ability to harness and manipulate cosmic energy. Her control over the celestial forces makes her a formidable force in the fight against evil. Despite her extraordinary powers, Supernova maintains a strong sense of justice and compassion. She uses her abilities to protect the innocent and uphold interdimensional law and order. Supernova's presence in the Rick and Morty universe showcases the diversity and complexity of its superhero landscape.
